2052.subject: VIET
2052.descrlong: Alternative assessment for the first semester of Vietnamese. Junior and senior transfers attempting to satisfy the Language ULR through assessment, must enroll in VIET 101, 102, and 201, except for international students who may enroll only in VIET 201 or 202.
